SLS 251ES-4 ORIGINAL
SB NO. 2
1 contained in joint resolutions concurred in by each house of the legislature during the 2025
2 Regular Session of the Legislature of Louisiana.
3 Section 2. The election for which provision is made in this Act shall be held in
4 compliance with and subject to the applicable provisions of the Louisiana Election Code.
5 Section 3. Section 2 of Act No. 218 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
6 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
7 Section 2. Be it further resolved that this proposed amendment shall be
8 submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at a statewide election to be held
9 on April 18, 2026, if House Bill No. 625 of the 2025 Regular Session of the
10 Legislature of Louisiana becomes effective. If House Bill No. 625 of the 2025
11 Regular Session of the Legislature of Louisiana does not become effective, this
12 proposed amendment shall be submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at
13 a statewide election to be held on November 3, 2026. May 16, 2026.
14 Section 4. Section 2 of Act No. 219 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
15 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
16 Section 2. Be it further resolved that this proposed amendment shall be
17 submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at the statewide election to be held
18 on April 18, 2026. May 16, 2026.
19 Section 5. Section 3 of Act No. 221 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
20 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
21 Section 3. Be it further resolved that this proposed amendment shall be
22 submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at the statewide election to be held
23 on April 18, 2026. May 16, 2026.
24 Section 6. Section 8 of Act No. 222 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
25 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
26 Section 8. Be it further resolved that this proposed amendment shall be
27 submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at the statewide election to be held
28 on April 18, 2026. May 16, 2026.
29 Section 7. Section 2 of Act No. 223 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
