SLS 251ES-4 ORIGINAL
SB NO. 2
Effective upon signature of the governor or lapse of time for gubernatorial action.
(Amends Act No. 218, §2; No. 219, §2; No. 221, §3; No. 222, §8; and No. 223, §2 all of the
2025 Regular Session; repeals Act 212 of the 2025 Regular Session)
